title: Dieudonné Kalulika
text:
Dieudonné Kalulika (born October 1, 1981) is a <a href="Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo">Congo</a>lese former <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player who last played for <a href="C.S.%20Vis%C3%A9">C.S. Visé</a>.
International career.
He was part of the Congolese <a href="2004%20African%20Nations%20Cup">2004 African Nations Cup</a> team that finished bottom of their group in the first round of competition, thus failing to qualify for the quarter-finals.
